Jaden Christopher Syre Smith -LRB- born July 8 , 1998 -RRB- is an American actor and rapper .
He is the son of Jada Pinkett Smith and Will Smith .
Jaden Smith 's first movie role was with his father in the 2006 film The Pursuit of Happyness .
He also acted in the 2008 remake of The Day the Earth Stood Still and the 2010 remake of The Karate Kid .
He was also in the 2013 film After Earth with his father .